<p class="lead">
Your members will love the added opportunities that box leagues create. It gives them an ongoing way to play challenges against similarly ranked players while allowing flexibility to schedule matches based around their schedules. At the end of a box cycle, SportyHQ makes it <em>simple</em> to start your next box cycle, with auto-promotion/demotion of players and features that let you quickly add, remove and move players from boxes.
